# Placeholder so this directory exists for Tauri resource bundling.
#
# At release time, CI populates this directory with the small, essential
# embedding models that must be present on first launch:
#   - all-MiniLM-L6-v2.onnx   (text embeddings, 384-d — the active contract)
#   - tokenizer.json          (MiniLM tokenizer)
#   - clip-vit-base-patch32-vision_q4.onnx  (image embeddings for visual search)
#
# These are copied into <Resources>/models/ in the .app and seeded into the
# user's app-data models directory on first run (see seed_bundled_models in
# src-tauri/src/main.rs). The large Qwen3-VL GGUF + mmproj are downloaded
# in-app during onboarding instead of being bundled here.
#
# Model binaries are intentionally NOT committed (see .gitignore). Populate
# locally with: scripts/bootstrap/download-minilm.sh src-tauri/bundled-models
#               scripts/bootstrap/download-clip-vision-onnx.sh src-tauri/bundled-models
